Remember that this code assumes the binary data in the `ByteBuf` is structured as:  `[number of positions (unsigned short)][x1 (unsigned short)][y1 (unsigned short)][x2 (unsigned short)][y2 (unsigned short)]...`  Adjust the reading logic if your binary format is different.  You'll also need to include the Netty library in your project to use this code.

