            maxVotes,
            tiebreak.getExplanation());
      }
    }
  }

  for (String winner : selectedWinners) {
    Logger.info(
        "Candidate \"%s\" was elected in round %d with %s votes.",
        winner, currentRound, currentRoundTally.getCandidateTally(winner));
  }

